snippet.title: Splitgate - Official Console Release Date Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2021
snippet.description:
In a new trailer, it was revealed the Halo meets Portal shooter Splitgate will be coming to PS4, PS5, Xbox One, and Xbox Series X starting on July 27.

#IGN #Gaming #SummerOfGaming
